Part 53 - Exemptions (§ 53.1 to 53.2)

Part 56 - Cancelled Certificates (§ 56.1)

Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 20, ch. I, subch. G
Parts 50 through 56 contained in this Subchapter were
renumbered as part of a reorganization of the department's regulations. These

Parts were previously Parts 440 through
446. State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
